{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"366119-my-inside-weather","title":"Cuaca dalam Diriku","description":"Semua orang tahu bagaimana keadaan cuaca di luar, tetapi terkadang, suasana hati kita sulit dijelaskan.","language":"Bahasa Indonesia","langCode":"id","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Adani Nur Sabrina"],"illustrators":["Lara Berge"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Badan Pengembangan dan Pembinaan Bahasa","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/366119-my-inside-weather"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/85534/size3/6e8e6e5ebe8a509c6cac6b397e0ad36a.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/85534/size6/6e8e6e5ebe8a509c6cac6b397e0ad36a.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/85182/size6/d3618c2bc75dd49d0abe101147f52090.jpg","text":"Kita bisa dengan mudah mengetahui cuaca di luar, sekalipun cuaca itu berubah-ubah\n sepanjang waktu.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/85183/size6/4dadee9c8a45c6c9f0eae31f93d84142.jpg","text":"3/27","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/85184/size6/633c9a27c46ece5741cc4a0745c39744.jpg","text":"Namun, sulit untuk mengetahui cuaca yang ada dalam diriku. Terkadang, aku merasa tidak ada seorang pun yang bisa memahaminya.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/85185/size6/6ce02502af281ce0e11148aaad013973.jpg","text":"5/27","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/85186/size6/5bda2e65648e55af51057f20c13fa446.jpg","text":"Apakah kau pernah merasakannya juga?","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/85187/size6/96a611e586866702ffb35796fb8d870d.jpg","text":"7/27","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/85188/size6/cdd5f96d82477a647312f5b8f13b42b5.jpg","text":"Ada kalanya pikiranku penuh dengan sinar mentari dan pelangi yang indah. Aku merasa sanggup melakukan apa pun.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/85189/size6/49192e2654f8756f9e190147806b56b2.jpg","text":"9/27","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/85190/size6/5aa033ad699501fcf1e9214cd06c84cc.jpg","text":"Pada waktu lain, kepalaku bisa dipenuhi kabut dan awan tebal. Aku jadi sulit \nmengingat banyak hal atau mendengar \napa yang orang lain katakan.","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/85191/size6/c70c95a188fa2147eb6e649da4f91031.jpg","text":"11/27","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/85192/size6/c3181b48c7dca0ab1f45df8e9ddc00ee.jpg","text":"Terkadang, aku bangun tidur \ndengan angin ribut menyesaki kepalaku. \nAku merasa sangat lelah dan mudah tersinggung.","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/85193/size6/e071e1144cac9ae81b80a548850b0337.jpg","text":"13/27","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/85194/size6/e038b8379814276232cef9ad6e58cca0.jpg","text":"Aku juga kadang-kadang merasa ada hujan di dalam diriku. Hujan itu bisa menjelma menjadi\ngerimis kecil yang membuatku sedih, \natau badai hebat yang membuatku marah.","words":null},{"n":14,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/85195/size6/23477d3e0d0057bdf9e0f999484ee00b.jpg","text":"15/27","words":null},{"n":15,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/85196/size6/3deee50446fa6d1cb246c512258a3213.jpg","text":"Terkadang, cuaca dalam diriku \ntidak sama seperti cuaca \nyang ada di luar.","words":null},{"n":16,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/85197/size6/86c6d2357d53589d3fb0094c5f169ea7.jpg","text":"17/27","words":null},{"n":17,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/85198/size6/bccd428ed3190a74b6a20f2b89079326.jpg","text":"Terkadang, cuaca dalam diriku \ntidak sesuai dengan apa yang ingin kurasakan\natau apa yang seharusnya kurasakan.","words":null},{"n":18,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/85199/size6/0d9c4d3ad4687785e9445fb6f94a85ab.jpg","text":"19/27","words":null},{"n":19,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/85200/size6/958a2534f5565617118c5e99540a9c8f.jpg","text":"Apakah itu baik-baik saja? \nTentu.","words":null},{"n":20,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/85201/size6/5b23b326b6c98f21e3e60c4a9703c128.jpg","text":"21/27","words":null},{"n":21,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/85202/size6/cb1b5568372126df022150fd0572d12e.jpg","text":"Hal terbaik yang bisa kita lakukan ketika merasa cuaca dalam diri kita tidak menentu \nadalah dengan membicarakannya bersama \norang yang kita sayangi.","words":null},{"n":22,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/85203/size6/e56d888954f44cc75d4a19739b7a2c56.jpg","text":"23/27","words":null},{"n":23,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/85204/size6/797295a5f1a5ff32fbcd0aeeec8dcb52.jpg","text":"Mereka juga punya cuaca dalam dirinya.\nJadi, mereka bisa memahaminya.","words":null},{"n":24,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/85205/size6/a92bdbe1975a7c8e22e88ba5ca879277.jpg","text":"25/27","words":null},{"n":25,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/85206/size6/d9ed464a3b3643fe9f88409ec997d334.jpg","text":"26/27","words":null},{"n":26,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/85207/size6/54f54ff62e15de4dea7fdd02b7bbfe41.jpg","text":"27/27","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":26,"words":198}}